## How to attribute

If you use or adapt content from this repository, a suitable attribution would be:

> *“Based on the OpSec Documentation Hub by [Effjy](https://github.com/effjy/opsec), licensed under CC BY-NC-SA 4.0.”*

If you have modified the content, add a note such as:

> *“This document contains modifications from the original.”*

